{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":72,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"每个人自出娘胎后，便要和别人竞争，想出人头地，自要付出代价。不过创业虽难，守成则更难，邦国如是，武功亦如是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":152,"line_start":2,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"假若我们能在今晚这种没有可能的情况下，抓走上官龙，岂非痛快之极。","tone":"激动","chapter":152,"line_start":8,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"这世上没有不可能的事。但问题是上官龙既为阴癸派的重要人物，手底下定是很硬，我们却要活擒他，一趟不成以后便休想再能攻其不备，所以没有七、八成把握，亦不宜轻举妄动。","tone":"认真","chapter":152,"line_start":12,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"只要他落了单我们便有办法，他怎都强不过边不负吧！","tone":"陈述","chapter":152,"line_start":16,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"上官龙肯定是老奸巨猾的人、否则也不能在阴癸派坐上这重要职位。即使宋二公子肯帮我们，也休想可把他骗到无人的地方下手。","tone":"认真","chapter":152,"line_start":18,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"他上茅厕时总不能也大批人前呼后拥吧？","tone":"调侃","chapter":152,"line_start":24,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"首先你要肯定他会于何时和会到何处方便。只是这宝贵情报已是不易取得，还要他真个前去才行。咦！","tone":"轻笑","chapter":152,"line_start":30,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_ba_feng_han","text":"不要那么瞧我，我只是隐约把握到些甚么似的，却毫不实在。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":152,"line_start":38,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"横竖我们现在一筹莫展，你何不说来听听。","tone":"陈述","chapter":152,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我们之所以把目标定在上官龙身上，皆因他在阴癸派身份够高，知晓很多阴癸派的机密，必要时尚可用他来交换瑜姨。但问题若只是要肯定瑜姨的行踪下落，抓起上官龙左右手那类的人物，亦可以清楚这方面的消息，但却容易多了。","tone":"认真","chapter":152,"line_start":44,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"只要肯定瑜姨没有落在阴癸派手上，今晚我就挑战上官龙，取他狗命。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":152,"line_start":50,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"曲傲则交由我负责好了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":152,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"这样把事情闹大，只对我们有害无利。如果涫妖女或边不负扮作上官龙的手下出来应战，仲少仍这么有把握吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":152,"line_start":56,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"有师妃暄这大敌窥伺在旁，涫妖女怎会轻易出手，至于对付边不负，我寇仲未必全无取胜的希望。","tone":"大笑","chapter":152,"line_start":62,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"此计实是可行之极。边不负一向深藏不露，在这种情况下更绝不会现身露脸。","tone":"认真","chapter":152,"line_start":66,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"我有办法了！","tone":"激动","chapter":152,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"寇仲你给我滚出来！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":152,"line_start":72,"line_end":72}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_kou_zhong","name":"寇仲","alias":["仲少"],"identity":"少帅军首领","faction":"少帅军","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"与徐子陵并称「双龙」的少帅军首领，志在争霸天下","personality":{"traits":["机智果敢","幽默风趣","重情重义","胆大妄为","争强好胜","果决刚毅"],"speech_style":"豪爽直率，常带调侃","temperament":"热血冲动但不失谋略"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xu_zi_ling","type":"挚友","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"生死之交"},{"target":"char_song_yu_zhi","type":"恋人","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"互有情意"},{"target":"char_ba_feng_han","type":"合作者","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"并肩作战"},{"target":"char_bian_bu_fu","type":"宿敌","intensity":75,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"生死相搏"},{"target":"char_shang_guan_long","type":"对手","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"计划擒拿"}],"known_skills":["skill_chang_sheng_jue","skill_jing_zhong_yue"],"related_skills":["skill_shao_shuai_qiang"],"rag_refs